OL,5, A public inquiry into the mistreatment 
OL,6, of immigration detainees has heard a   
OL,7, BBC Panorama documentary revealed      
OL,8, "shocking" treatment which had "no     
OL,9, place in a decent and humane" system.  
OL,11,FThe inquiry into Brook House removal   
OL,12,Fcentre, near Gatwick, is examining     
OL,13,Fmistreatment of detainees, as well as  
OL,14,Fthe attitudes and culture of staff.    
OL,16,FIt follows a series of investigations  
OL,17,Ftriggered by Panorama in 2017.         
OL,19,FAt the time, G4S ran the Sussex centre,
OL,20,Fbut Serco took it over last year.      
